relation: Darrow1 - #40 After a disturbing dream, Jeff awakens to find he's slept the night away. Also, a familiar face appears.
Darrow1 - #41 The legendary Tessie appears, though her part is rather brief, she's still happy to get her name out there. Fame is a hard business.
Darrow1 - #42 Sailing to southern Winters ends in success and all that's left is to get to Dr. Andonuts' lab. Easy enough, right?
Darrow1 - #43 With a pencil-shaped road block keeping Jeff from passing, the only option is the strange dungeon Brick Road. But what starts as fun and games...may end in a mad duck massacre.

I had an old piece of art I used as a placeholder for the comic's title and finally decided to put a real title page up. The hardest part of this was deciding on how I wanted the text, so I made two versions: One for the comic and one for fanart.
